{"tid":158934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個遇過最恐怖既經歷","createTime":"2017-03-16T15:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T15:49:36.000Z","uid":91643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94893824a20f90c64a44b5766fe8fb4f78b6c62a","tid":158934,"uid":91643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:31:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n我先。<br />\n<br />\n話說細細個既時候，同老豆去探住係山上面<br />\n既嬤嬤，佢都住得算偏僻。<br />\n<br />\n由於係冬天，個時黃昏5點個天已經接近黑曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。老豆翻開地盤工，有架專門用黎上山既吉普車(個轆好大，後面掛個後備軚個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n嬤嬤住粉嶺流水響個邊，咁我同爸爸系車，已經過左一座叫龍山寺既寺廟(細細個老母千叮萬囑六點後唔比去個邊玩，傳聞好邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )。記得個時仲聽緊收音機啲阿叔尻up。突然見到有個啊伯系條山路到行，著仲件藍色唐裝衫，戴住清朝帽，手持拐杖。佢烏低身拐下拐下，見唔到樣。(個時已經覺得奇怪，個頭都想偏僻，正常唔會有人行路，多數搭小巴或揸車)咁我老豆見佢自己一個，行動不便，睇下要唔要幫手，就停車開窗問:[伯伯，食左飯未？去邊啊？] 個伯伯冇應，繼續烏住身行。咁我老豆又八卦，伸個頭出車窗，向後望。。。<br />\n<br />\n我老豆冇出聲，閂翻車窗，開車走。事後問翻，佢話個伯伯已經唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到而家都印象深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4edb07d879700f4b457ac5a315a6409040bb8dff","tid":158934,"uid":91643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G02a7Bn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG02a7Bn.jpg&h=a0d1e5ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/234912_8699d0749fda451a5d11c4c4bf5bfed9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F234912_8699d0749fda451a5d11c4c4bf5bfed9.jpg&h=1f7b8db5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伯伯服裝大概係咁"}]}